#: app/templates/admin/index.html:9
msgid "Admin Panel"
msgstr "لوحة التحكم"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:11
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Grylli Admin Panel. Use the tools below to manage users, "
"configuration, and infrastructure-related settings."
